4px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot; segoe ui helvetica arial sans-serif white-space: normal background-color: rgb&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/9337488-f6099b17395ebe40.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; title=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: content-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; max-width: 100%; height: auto;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;ul style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 2em; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot; segoe ui helvetica arial sans-serif white-space: normal background-color: rgb class=&quot; list-paddingleft-2&quot;&gt;\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n&lt;ul style=&quot;list-style-type: square;&quot; class=&quot; list-paddingleft-2&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;*&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;/ul&gt;\n&lt;h3 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 24px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.25em; line-height: 1.25; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot; segoe ui helvetica arial sans-serif white-space: normal background-color: rgb&gt;5. del标签&lt;/h3&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot; segoe ui helvetica arial sans-serif white-space: normal background-color: rgb&gt;HTML &lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;text-decoration:line-through;&quot;&gt;元素定义了删除（移除）文字。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, &quot; segoe ui helvetica arial sans-serif white-space: normal